      },
      "date": "2015-05-01 21:59:09.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n\nThis patch works, however the test is not enough. The test 37 by itself passes with or without the rest of the patch on a single host, and so is meaningless. The original bug report has 2 clients (one for the test, and one for the copytool). I created a /mnt/lustre2 mountpoint and mounted the fs, then changed the test setup to\n\n\tcopytool_cleanup\n\tcopytool_setup $SINGLEAGT /mnt/lustre2\n\nwhich simulate 2 clients. The failure can be reproduced with this setup, and the patch fixes it.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
